[{"title":"Entertain","key":"8","dataProvider":null,"subtitle":"Put on a bash, raise some cash.","backgroundImage":"/images/lennySquare.jpg","content":"<p>Comic Relief is a major charity based in the UK which strives to create a just world free from poverty – and we work 365 days a year to help that vision become a reality.</p><h2 class=\"h3\">Our mission is to drive positive change through the power of entertainment. </h2><p>Since we first set up shop in 1985, we’ve been doing three main things…</p><ul><li>We raise millions of pounds through two big fundraising campaigns – Red Nose Day and Sport Relief.</li><li>We spend that money in the best possible way to tackle the root causes of poverty and social injustice.</li><li>We use the power of our brand to raise awareness of the issues that we care most about.</li></ul><p>Over the years we’ve inspired a lot of people who don’t normally ‘do’ charity to, well, do charity.&nbsp; The support we’ve had from so many friends has always blown us away – and still does today.</p>","type":"articlefeature","param1":null,"param2":null,"description":null,"url":null,"id":null,"providerid":null,"hideimage":false,"maxitems":0},{"title":"Dress Up","key":"9","dataProvider":null,"subtitle":"Look fabulous like moi!","backgroundImage":"/images/piggySquare.jpg","content":"<p>Hold a <strong>glammed-up Day at work</strong> &amp; get people to donate to bling it up.</p><div class=\"field-group-format group_tip field-group-div group-tip  speed-none effect-none\"><p>Get more people to take part by offering a prize for the best dressed.</p><p>Get sponsored to have a bad-taste clothes day.</p><div class=\"field-group-format group_tip field-group-div group-tip  speed-none effect-none\"><p>Collect money on a <a href=\"http://my.rednoseday.com/registration\" target=\"_blank\">Red Nose Day Giving Page</a> — &amp; the safe and secure way to get sponsored.</p></div><div class=\"field-group-format group_ides_tips field-group-div group-ides-tips  speed-none effect-none\"><div class=\"field-group-format group_idea field-group-div group-idea  speed-none effect-none\"><p>Get a Red Nose, T-shirt and other goodies to look the part and top up your fundraising.</p></div><p class=\"field-group-format group_tip field-group-div group-tip  speed-none effect-none\">See the <a href=\"http://www.rednoseday.com/sites/rednoseday.com/files/downloadables/rnd13_shopping_list.pdf\" target=\"_blank\">full range</a> available and do good while you shop</p></div><h2>Did you know...</h2><div class=\"field-group-format group_content_wrapper field-group-div group-content-wrapper  speed-none effect-none\"><div class=\"field-group-format group_content field-group-div group-content  speed-none effect-none\"><div class=\"field-group-format group_copy field-group-div group-copy  speed-none effect-none\"><p>You can get Red Nose Day goodies on the high street. Sainsbury’s and Oxfam sell Noses and more, and TK Maxx sell our T-shirts.</p></div></div></div></div>","type":"article","param1":null,"param2":null,"description":null,"url":null,"id":null,"providerid":null,"hideimage":false,"maxitems":0},{"title":"Bake","key":"11","dataProvider":null,"subtitle":"Bake with Mary","backgroundImage":"/images/bake.jpg","content":"<p><strong>Hold a cake sale</strong> for a tried-and-tested way to fundraise.</p><div class=\"field-group-format group_tip field-group-div group-tip  speed-none effect-none\"><p>Ask everyone to get baking too - the more you bake, the more money you’ll make.</p></div><div class=\"field-group-format group_ides_tips field-group-div group-ides-tips  speed-none effect-none\"><div class=\"field-group-format group_idea field-group-div group-idea  speed-none effect-none\"><p>Get people to <strong>bring in their best dish</strong> for a lunch buffet, and everyone pays to tuck in.</p></div><div class=\"field-group-format group_tip field-group-div group-tip  speed-none effect-none\"><p>Make sure you have a variety of dishes to satisfy everyone’s tastes.</p></div></div><div class=\"field-group-format group_ides_tips field-group-div group-ides-tips  speed-none effect-none\"><div class=\"field-group-format group_idea field-group-div group-idea  speed-none effect-none\"><p>Charge people to guess how many sweets are in a jar or what a cake weighs.</p></div><div class=\"field-group-format group_tip field-group-div group-tip  speed-none effect-none\"><p>Fool people by baking a lighter-than-light Maltesers cake using our recipe:</p><h2>Let your lighter side out in the kitchen this Red Nose Day</h2><div class=\"news-media\"><img alt=\"\" src=\"http://d3omxesufncgl0.cloudfront.net/cdn/farfuture/tc48ymLH9KSjReBr3jA2bpw1nxEgmsTdxmREs9LPRb8/deploymtime:1362590849/sites/rednoseday.com/files/styles/news-landscape/public/resizedMalt-Cake.jpg?itok=RFfHhFhl\" /></div><p>The best way to raise money is by having fun. So this Red Nose Day, let out your lighter side and get baking with <a href=\"http://www.rednoseday.com/partners/maltesers\">Maltesers</a>.</p><p>Maltesers is aiming to raise £1 million for Comic Relief, so pop on your apron and enjoy this lovely cake!</p><p><strong>Maltesers® Chocolate Delight</strong></p><p><strong>Serves 12</strong></p><p><strong>For the base</strong></p><ul><li><strong>180g</strong> Unsalted butter, softened</li><li><strong>180g</strong> Golden caster sugar</li><li><strong>3</strong> Eggs</li><li><strong>180g</strong> Self-raising flour</li><li><strong>25g</strong> Malted milk powder</li><li><strong>25g</strong> Cocoa powder</li><li><strong>4 tbsp</strong> Milk</li><li><strong>For the filling/topping</strong></li><li><strong>250g</strong><span> Icing sugar</span></li><li><strong>40g</strong> Malted milk powder</li><li><strong>25g</strong> Cocoa powder</li><li><strong>125g</strong> Unsalted butter, softened</li><li><strong>2 tbsp</strong> Boiling water</li><li><strong>135g</strong> Maltesers®</li></ul><ol><li><span>Preheat your oven to 180ºC/160ºC fan/Gas 4.</span></li><li><span>Grease and line two 18cm round sandwich tins.</span></li><li><span>Beat your butter and sugar in a bowl until light and fluffy.</span></li><li><span>Next, add the eggs, flour, malted milk and cocoa powder, and milk, then beat until smooth and creamy.</span></li><li><span>Split the mix between your tins and bake for 25 mins.</span></li><li><span>When your cakes are firm, pop them out and allow to cool.</span></li></ol><p><strong>Extremely Chocolaty Icing</strong><span>&nbsp;</span></p><ol><li><strong><span>Pop your icing sugar, malted milk and cocoa powder in a food processor, and pulse a few times.</span></strong></li><li><strong><span>Add the butter to your mix and pulse again.</span></strong></li><li><strong><span>Pour in the boiling water and mix until it’s nice and gooey. Add a little more water if you need to.</span></strong></li><li><strong><span>Scoop half the icing into a small bowl, then blend 35g of Maltesers® into tiny pieces.</span></strong></li><li><strong><span>Mix your Maltesers® in the icing and spread over one of the sponges.</span></strong></li><li><strong><span>Place the second sponge on top and cover with the remaining icing.</span></strong></li><li><strong><span>Have fun sprinkling on your Maltesers® to finish.</span></strong></li></ol></div></div>","type":"article","param1":null,"param2":null,"description":null,"url":null,"id":null,"providerid":null,"hideimage":false,"maxitems":0},{"title":"Zac is in on it too","key":"12","dataProvider":null,"subtitle":"My Son Zac dressing up","backgroundImage":"/images/zacSquare.jpg","content":"Zac is in on it!!!","type":"article","param1":null,"param2":null,"description":null,"url":null,"id":null,"providerid":null,"hideimage":false,"maxitems":0}]